{
  "stem": "25651.10",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The way this was done was that every time an SS officer came into the kleiderkammer, Nitka would offer to sew for him a uniform.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they really had-- some of them had uniforms made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Nitka would always made-- make them very tight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He, anyway, was a tight tailor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He, he-- somehow, everything was tight-fitting with Nitka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he made these uniforms, and he would always have a bit of cloth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, if you would have two bits of cloth, he says-- he would show me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, he'd have them sort of underneath all the other [NON-ENGLISH] that he had stored.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there would be German uniform cloth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- he'd say, look, here I have the back, and here I have the two fronts, you see, for the jacket.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I've got one sleeve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I need another sleeve, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next uniform, I'll get the sleeve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then I'll have the jacket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then comes the trousers, so then we're there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we've got the hat to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The hat will be the most complicated because of the insignia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, that was Nitka's thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like, at some time in the future, Rudy would escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Meanwhile, Rudy would get hold of girls and go to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, Rudy says to the two of us, come, I'll talk to my girlfriend, and she'll find girlfriends for you two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, we are in the mannerlager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How will you talk to your girlfriend?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So, he says, oh, if we go behind, she'll-- she's in the C, C camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they're all Hungarian girls there, and they'll come to the wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'll tell my girlfriend to bring some young girls for you-- for you two.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
